{
  "stem": "10829.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But still being in the town, on the third section, they pushed everybody in, and we had to move over from the center house, and we had to move.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Mom and I and my sister and my brother, we were pushed over to a house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And luckily, we were into a house that belonged to my cousin, my mother's aunt.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we knew the house well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we stayed down there for a while.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you used to go out every day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You used to go out and do the work.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We still had to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had to provide food and work the fields and milk the cows and-- for-- for-- to give the-- the soldiers and all them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were eating, and they were killing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a very rough time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the way they were set up, for instance, we went to-- when you get up in the morning, you go to work real early.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And our streets where was the-- was-- had posts on each side.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was a soldier or somebody with a rifle would sit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And as you walk towards the graves when you did your-- finished your work, when you went there, and you went back, you had to go from one to other ones, like zigzag in the street.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And they would all [INAUDIBLE] you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And the women was-- men were not hurt as bad as most of the women.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They used to take the kids and the women, and they used to rape them right down there or else kill them or cut them apart.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This-- the-- the-- the-- the-- more vicious harm they could do, these young Ukraines, I mean, the more they were rewarded.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was just plain simple.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
